{"tid":747046,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"批評家的消亡正是文明退步的象徵。","createTime":"2018-07-18T05:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T11:24:52.000Z","uid":105678,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b50592d495c368a839618b02ab9f9bb1d47ed8d1","tid":747046,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:28:15.000Z","msg":"真理從來都是出自於爭辯，正如古希臘的<br />\n哲人論道，求的是接近真理的法則，雖互有競爭和惡言相向，但透過近乎比賽嘅論戰，人發現自身不足，進而不斷完善。<br />\n<br />\n到現代，人與人之間反之以和氣為上，容許錯誤、異質存在，他們認為批評就是haters，講壞話，拒絕傾聽。當然，心水清者必然樂於接受批評，並於內心思考真偽。<br />\n<br />\n當世界不再批評意見而允許虛偽的和氣時，將是一場絕世浩劫，漫天鬼怪，萬物之靈的寶座必再次騰空。"},{"pid":"36d5c8defa38fc7c73d2c4ddc2ecc31f673daae3","tid":747046,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:31:09.000Z","msg":"Haters係理性批評咩？"},{"pid":"500603352cdf7c1bdd4137069436e028413bc5bf","tid":747046,"uid":105678,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"36d5c8defa38fc7c73d2c4ddc2ecc31f673daae3","tid":747046,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:31:09.000Z","msg":"Haters係理性批評咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:33:40.000Z","msg":"When u hear something that u dont want hear, it is the hater."},{"pid":"49ce46a727a29f648b938ba240b3d5e93ec478c3","tid":747046,"uid":191633,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"36d5c8defa38fc7c73d2c4ddc2ecc31f673daae3","tid":747046,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:31:09.000Z","msg":"Haters係理性批評咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:39:48.000Z","msg":"haters嘅存在係有必要而且係良性嘅<br />\n無haters你嘅世界只會得一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個場你玩晒係一件苦悶嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且個場唔會有突破性嘅進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n